high_descs: Walk across the room to the window, then turn right and walk over to the counter.
Pick up the metal butter knife off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the counter on the other side of the room.
Slice up the tomato on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter in the middle of the leftmost sponge.
Pick up the end slice of tomato off of the counter.
Turn left and walk over to the stove.
Put the tomato slice in the large metal bowl that is on the back left burner of the stove.
Pick up the large metal bowl with the tomato slice in it.
Turn left and walk over to the small white table in the corner of the room.
Place the large metal bowl with the tomato slice in it onto the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a metal bowl with a tomato slice inside on a white table.

high_descs: Walk to the window, turn right to face counter.
Pick up knife from counter.
Turn so back is to counter, walk to counter in front of you.
Slice tomato that is on counter.
Put knife down on top of sponge on the left of counter.
Pick up one tomato slice from counter.
Turn left, walk to stove, turn right to face stove.
Put tomato slice in pot on left back burner.
Pick up pot with tomato slice.
Turn left, walk to door, turn right to face table.
Put pot on right back corner of table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooking pot with a tomato slice in it on a table.

high_descs: walk forwards to the end of the room, then turn right and walk over to the kitchen counter ahead
grab the butter knife off of the counter there
turn around and walk forwards to the kitchen counter
chop up the tomato on top of the counter
place the butter knife down on top of the sponge on the left
grab a tomato slice off of the counter
turn left and walk over to the left side of the stove on the right
place the tomato slice in the pan on the stove on the back left burner
grab the pan off of the burner
turn left and walk forwards to the end of the room, then turn right to face the kitchen table there
place the pan down on the kitchen table there
anns.task_desc: place a pan with a tomato slice inside down on the kitchen table

high_descs: walk forward to the wall then turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward to face the counter.
Cut the tomato on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on the counter.
Pick up a tomato slice from on the counter.
Take a step to the left and face the pot on the back left burner.
Put the tomato slice into the pot on the back left corner.
Pick up the pot with the tomato slice in it.
Turn to the left, walk across the room, then turn right to face the table.
Place the pot with tomato slice in it on the table.
anns.task_desc: To cut a tomato slice plus putting it into a pot as well as moving the pot from the stove to a table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the dishwasher.
Grab the knife that is behind the kettle and to the left.
With the knife in hand turn around and go to the counter that is directly behind you.
With the knife slice the tomato that is on the counter.
Set the knife down on the sponge that is on the left.
Pick up a slice of tomato that is closest to you.
With the slice of tomato in hand go to the stove.
Place the slice of tomato in the pot that is on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the tomato in it.
Turn left and go to the table with the pot and tomato in hand.
Place the pot with tomato on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Slice tomato to put in pot.

high_descs: Go to the counter next to the sink.
Pick up a knife on the counter.
Turn and go to the counter by the stove.
Cut the tomato on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn and go to the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in a pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot on the stove.
Turn left and go to the table by the door.
Put the pot on the table by the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a pot from the stove to the table by the door.
